      <title>美联储储备降至 3 万亿美元以下，为 2020 年以来的最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/reserves-at-fed-sink-below-3-trillion-to-the-lowest-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行体系储备金是美联储决定继续缩减资产负债表的一个关键因素，该储备金已跌破3万亿美元，降至2020年10月以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-03/reserves-at-fed-sink-below-3-trillion-to-the-lowest-since-2020</guid>
